    //1. Constructor
         =>setting value of Global variables
         =>multiple variable values is set in one go
         =>will have to provide values to all the parameters of the constructor

    //2. setter method-->
         a) assigning
            =>setting value of Global variables
            =>One variable value is set at a time
            =>Can assign value to the variables which we wish to
         b) updating the values

    //3. Builder Pattern
       => setting the value

    //4. Pass By Reference-->updating the values